Ingredients:

    Pizza dough
    1 cup tomato sauce
    1 bell pepper, thinly sliced
    1 red onion, thinly sliced
    1 cup cherry tomatoes, halved
    1 cup mushrooms, sliced
    1 cup black olives, sliced
    1 1/2 cups mozzarella cheese, shredded
    Olive oil

Instructions:

    Preheat your oven.
    Roll out the pizza dough.
    Spread tomato sauce evenly over the dough.
    Distribute sliced bell pepper, red onion, cherry tomatoes, mushrooms, and black olives.
    Sprinkle mozzarella cheese on top.
    Drizzle with olive oil.
    Bake until the crust is golden and the cheese is melted.
    Allow it to cool slightly before slicing.

Don't forget to add a spoon of love!
